{"tid":189534,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【絕望】要醒了，要開始搵工返了","createTime":"2017-04-06T13:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T13:33:05.000Z","uid":43804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"018df71b598eb8aa34f64a43871da73811212833","tid":189534,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"想搵個地方呻下sosad<br />\n<br />\n辭工差唔多兩個月，去左個幾禮拜台灣旅行，聽日就要返香港了，覺得好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好唔想做嘢，唔想過返嗰種唔撚係人過嘅生活，喺台灣呢段時間我先覺得自己似個人。但奈何有家要養，又不能瀟灑得太耐，去個幾禮拜已經比屋企人哦，返黎要搵工喇乜乜乜&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n唉，人生到底係為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600715abd41e7f6c39ccb7f26482fcf18c88a1ba","tid":189534,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nI know that feel bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11398bd8ca8e46226e1031796712e254a0f598b7","tid":189534,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"你老豆係窮人<br />\n<br />\n咁多性幻想做乜鳩"}]}